    <string name="privacy_policy">PRIVACY POLICY AND LEGAL NOTICE\n\nDeambulario is committed to protecting user privacy. By using this application, you consent to the processing of your data according to the following conditions:\n\nGoogle Maps API: This app uses Google Maps services for route visualization and geolocation. Use of this feature is subject to the Google Maps Additional Terms of Service and the Google Privacy Policy.\n\nLocation Data Processing: To ensure the core functionality of the routes, the app collects precise location data, even when the app is in the background or closed (only while a session is active). This data is used exclusively to allow real-time tracking by the responsible teacher and is not shared with third parties outside the Firebase/Google service.\n\nPurpose: The data collected (nicknames, activity responses, and geolocation) is used for strictly educational and safety purposes during field activities.</string>
